        <p><span class="font-weight-bold">“Risk Period</span> has the meaning set out in clause 5.3.</p>

        <p class="font-weight-bold">2. ACCEPTANCE</p>
        <p>2.1 The Conditions apply to the Contract to the exclusion of any other terms that the Customer seeks to
