        <p class="font-weight-bold">Terms & Conditions of Rental of Rental item</p>
        <p class="font-weight-bold">4. DELIVERY</p>
        <p>4.1 <b>Rent’emAll</b> shall deliver the Rental item to the location set out in the Order or such other
