          remain at the sole risk of the Customer during the Rental Period and any further term during which the Rental
          item is in the possession, custody or control of the Customer (<span class="font-weight-bold">“Risk Period</span>)
          until such time as the Rental
          item is returned to <b>Rent’emAll</b>.</p>

        <p class="font-weight-bold">6. TRAINING</p>
        <p>6.1 The Customer represents and acknowledges that he has requisite knowledge and experience to operate the
          Rental item.</p>
        <p>6.2 <b>Rent’emAll</b> representatives may be called upon to provide start up operator training for the
